Simple clock utilites for Plan 9

eggclock.c: A simple eggclock. Invoke with ./8.eggclock <timeout in secs>. 
Controls:
Space pauses the countdown.
'q' exits the program.

The eggclock will exit with an exit string of alarm if the timeout has been reached. 
See eggclock_example.rc how to check this.

stopwatch.c: A simple stopwatch.
Controls:
Space stops/starts the clock.
'q' exits the program.
'r' resets the clock to 0:00:00 and logs the time before the reset to stdout.

